Package cycleguard.database.packs

Class PackData

java.lang.Object
cycleguard.database.AbstractDatabaseEntry
cycleguard.database.packs.PackData
public final class PackData extends AbstractDatabaseEntry
DynamoDbBean linking a pack to its data.
  • Primary key: name - Name of pack
  • hashedPassword - Encrypted password of goal, used to join
  • owner - Username of the pack's owner
  • memberList - List of usernames that are members of the pack, including the owner
  • invites - Users currently invited to the pack
  • packGoal - Current PackGoal of pack
